import functools
 
input_ = input().split()
k = int(input_[0])
n = int(input_[1])
 
dp = [0 for i in range(n + 1)]
dp[0] = 1
 
for i in range(1, n + 1):
    j = i
    while (j >= i - k and j >= 0):
        dp[i] += dp[j]
        j -= 1
         
print(dp[n])
